Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.59,Momoe,,0,0,560,,{\i0}Veni{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.59,Neiru,,1500,0,0,,{\i0}Veni{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.59,Rika Kawai,,0,1500,0,,{\i0}Veni{\i1}.
